  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c2df72f4760751d30153d473822aabf1a7c3d462f664aa7f7fdb8dc626dc7c40

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
